---
// Speaks to the engineer buyer-influencer: shows the artifact they take home.
// Distinct from ApplyPanel (in-app v3→v4 diff). This is what lands in their
// editor: a prompt file with cited changes, ready to ship.
// Intentionally no CTAs. CtaFooter is the single closing conversion band.
---

<section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="reveal mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <p
        class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] text-muted-foreground uppercase"
      >
        For the engineer who ships
      </p>
      <h2
        class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-3xl"
      >
        The artifact you take home.
      </h2>
      <p
        class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg"
      >
        Every blind review produces one file: the new prompt, with each change
        cited to the comment that drove it. Copy it, paste it, ship it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal-scale mt-10 lg:mt-12">
      <div
        class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-foreground/5"
      >
        <div
          class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-b border-border bg-muted/40 px-4 py-2.5 sm:px-5"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg
              width="14"
              height="14"
              viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              aria-hidden="true"
              class="text-muted-foreground"
            >
              <path
                fill="currentColor"
                d="M4 1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2.5 3v10A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 4 14.5h8a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5V5.621a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-.44-1.06l-3.12-3.122A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 8.878 1H4Z"
              />
            </svg>
            <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-muted-foreground">
              prompts/customer-support.md
            </span>
            <span
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-md bg-primary/10 px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] font-medium text-primary"
            >
              v3 &rarr; v4
            </span>
          </div>
          <span
            class="hidden font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-foreground/70 sm:inline"
          >
            via Blind Bench
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_minmax(240px,320px)]">
          <div class="border-b border-border lg:border-r lg:border-b-0">
            <pre
              class="m-0 overflow-x-auto bg-transparent p-5 font-mono text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-foreground/85 sm:p-6"
            ><code><span class="diff-line diff-line-removed"><span class="diff-marker">-</span> You are a <span class="diff-removed">helpful</span> customer support agent. Answer the user&rsquo;s <span class="diff-removed">question</span>.</span>
<span class="diff-line diff-line-added"><span class="diff-marker">+</span> You are a customer support agent.</span>
<span class="diff-line diff-line-added"><span class="diff-marker">+</span> <span class="diff-added">Be friendly and professional. Write like a helpful coworker,</span></span>
<span class="diff-line diff-line-added"><span class="diff-marker">+</span> <span class="diff-added">not a corporate robot.</span></span>
<span class="diff-line diff-line-added"><span class="diff-marker">+</span> <span class="diff-added">Avoid formal openers (&ldquo;Dear valued customer&rdquo;) and</span></span>
<span class="diff-line diff-line-added"><span class="diff-marker">+</span> <span class="diff-added">form-letter phrases (&ldquo;I understand your concern&rdquo;).</span></span>
<span class="diff-line diff-line-added"><span class="diff-marker">+</span> <span class="diff-added">Get to the point and be warm.</span></span></code></pre>
          </div>

          <aside class="bg-muted/20 p-5 sm:p-6">
            <p
              class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted-foreground"
            >
              Trace
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-3">
              <li class="space-y-1.5">
                <p
                  class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-foreground/80"
                >
                  &ldquo;Reads like a corporate form letter.&rdquo;
                </p>
                <p
                  class="font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-foreground"
                >
                  &rarr; v4 lines 4&ndash;5
                </p>
              </li>
              <li class="space-y-1.5">
                <p
                  class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-foreground/80"
                >
                  &ldquo;&lsquo;I understand your concern&rsquo; is filler.&rdquo;
                </p>
                <p
                  class="font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-foreground"
                >
                  &rarr; v4 lines 5&ndash;6
                </p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </aside>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3 border-t border-border bg-muted/20 px-4 py-3 sm:px-5"
        >
          <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-muted-foreground">
            Use your own API key. No per-seat billing.
          </span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-mono text-[11px] text-muted-foreground"
          >
            <svg
              width="12"
              height="12"
              viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                fill="currentColor"
                d="M4 1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2.5 3v9A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 4 13.5h6V12H4V3h7v3.5h1.5V3A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 11 1.5H4Z M13 8.5h-1V12H8.5v1H12v3.5h1V13h3.5v-1H13V8.5Z"
              />
            </svg>
            Copy markdown
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .diff-line {
    display: block;
    padding: 0.05em 0.25em;
    margin: 0 -0.25em;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
  .diff-line-removed {
    background-color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--step-3) 8%, transparent);
  }
  .diff-line-added {
    background-color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--primary) 6%, transparent);
  }
  .diff-marker {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 1ch;
    margin-right: 0.5ch;
    color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--muted-foreground) 80%, transparent);
    user-select: none;
  }
  .diff-line-removed .diff-marker {
    color: var(--step-3);
  }
  .diff-line-added .diff-marker {
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  .diff-removed {
    color: var(--step-3);
    text-decoration: line-through;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
    text-decoration-color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--step-3) 50%, transparent);
  }
  .diff-added {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
